<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta content="text/html"; charset="UTF-8"; http-equiv="Content Type">
</head>

<body>
	<h1>Welcome to the sample app, <%= @user.name %>!</h1>
	<p>
		Your user name is <%= @user.username %><br \>	
		Here is the confirmation code to access your page. Please follow the link below and enter the code to begin.<br \>
		Your confirmation code is: <%= @code %>. Please beware that this code will expire in one week. If you do not enter the code in that time, please go to the sign up page, and sign up again.<br \>
		Link: <%= link_to "sample_app", user_email_url %>
    </p>
		
	<p> Thanks! And have fun!</p>
</body>
</html> 
		
	